{
  "stem": "14715.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we brought them close to the pits, and we tipped those bodies into it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a horrible night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know how long I worked there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The hours were endless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] this was that night-- very little light.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I'll never forget the second day with the incident.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That a transport came in, and there were small children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they took some of those children, and they threw them in-- into the pits-- living children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was beyond my imagination.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't know-- I just collapsed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We worked there two nights, day and night, with very little food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And finally, they brought us back to camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When they brought us back to camp, there was a rumor going around that we're going to be living in the crematoriums on top of the ovens-- second floor.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "At that time, the kommando was 800 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the second day-- we rested up one day-- they actually brought us into the crematoriums, and they assigned us rooms where to stay and sleep, which was a little better than in the camps.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We did not have straw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We actually had boards what laid out some blankets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And our blankets to cover, and only two tiers-- one on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we worked 12-hour shifts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And being the youngest among the group, I was assigned by the Jewish kapo to clean the quarters of the Germans, which worked there in the offices.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Polished their boots.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I used to darn their socks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And luckily, I did not work too hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But I saw more misery than anybody else because they put people into a group.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "One did that, one did this.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
